<item>
            <title>[SPR-471] incorrect html in spring.vm</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-471</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In spring.vm, the springFormSingleSelect and springFormMultiSelect macros use selected=&quot;true&quot; in the options element rather than selected=&quot;selected&quot;. The resulting html is invalid.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.glasshaus.com/formsreference/select.htm&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.glasshaus.com/formsreference/select.htm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="10750">SPR-471</key>
            <summary>incorrect html in spring.vm</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.spring.io/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png">Bug</type>
